tiger in your passenger seat?

48:06.656 --> 48:09.158
Maybe.
Some lady tiger.

48:12.579 --> 48:13.746
How much?

48:13.830 --> 48:15.331
43,000, fully equipped.

48:15.415 --> 48:17.041
That all?

48:17.125 --> 48:18.835
Machine-gun
turrets are extra.

48:19.002 --> 48:22.005
He's a funny guy.
Come here, Manny.

48:23.923 --> 48:26.342
Bulletproof this, okay?

48:26.426 --> 48:28.511
And this here and here.

48:29.512 --> 48:31.014
