- And the windows.

48:33.516 --> 48:36.769
Get me a phone
with a scrambler.

48:36.853 --> 48:38.104
A scrambler.

48:38.187 --> 48:40.690
And a radio
with scanners

48:40.773 --> 48:42.775
to pick up flying saucers,
stuff like that.

48:42.859 --> 48:44.527
Don't forget
the fog lights.

48:44.611 --> 48:48.531
Oh. In case I get caught in a swamp.
That's a good idea.

48:51.618 --> 48:54.621
Get out of the way, lady!
I'm trying to drive here!

48:56.039 --> 48:58.374
I thought you were
taking me to Frank.

49:04.005 --> 49:06.507
We got an hour.
You hungry?

49:08.217 --> 49:10.011
