49:11.054 --> 49:12.722
Well, that figures.

49:14.891 --> 49:18.186
Check it out, Manny, okay?
And pay the guy.

49:18.478 --> 49:21.689
And you take a taxi.
Meet me at the track, okay?

49:21.856 --> 49:23.566
Good doing business with you.
Mr. Montana.

49:24.942 --> 49:26.402
Oh, God, man!

49:28.988 --> 49:31.407
