but I'm better now.</i>

01:26:59.820 --> 01:27:01.780
<i>I do Laurel and Hardy
in Spanish, too.</i>

01:27:04.742 --> 01:27:06.869
<i>That's the height of
culture, I assure you.</i>

01:27:06.994 --> 01:27:09.538
<i>But my favorite Cuban of all
