like that asshole

01:28:33.706 --> 01:28:34.999
you were
dancing with tonight.

01:28:35.082 --> 01:28:39.169
I like Fernando.
He's a fun guy and he's nice.

01:28:40.754 --> 01:28:43.674
And he knows how
to treat a woman.
All right?

01:28:43.924 --> 01:28:45.759
